Forrest Taylor https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Forrest_Taylor 0 Edwin Forrest Taylor (December 29, 1883 – February 19, 1965) was an American character actor whose artistic career spanned six different decades, from silents through talkies to the advent of color films.
